## Observability Validation Notes
- Log entries are visible in Django Admin for all tested scenarios.
- No unexpected errors or missing logs observed during normal or lockout conditions.
- Logging behavior is consistent across Verify and Create Account endpoints.

---

## Risks & Edge Considerations
- Rate‑limit testing depends on reliable reuse of the same IP address.
- Misconfiguration of logging filters could hide events outside Django Admin.
- Environmental differences could affect reproducibility of system error scenarios.

